* Cameroon: Meya oa Cameroon City o phatlalalitsoeng hore o roala maske o tla tlameha ho liehisa ho hasana ha coronavirus. <ref>Cameroon City Makes Wearing Mask Mandatory in Fight Against Coronavirus,VOA News, 7 April 2020.</ref>
